                    <comment id="13046598" author="jonm" created="Thu, 9 Jun 2011 16:03:41 +0100"  >Hi Bart, patch applied to trunk. I&amp;#39;ll also work on backporting this to the other release branches.&lt;br/&gt;
</comment>
